column2: SELECT   f.id as FIRST_id, f.ra as FIRST_ra, f.dec as FIRST_dec,   g.id as GLX_id, g.objid, g.ra as GLX_ra, g.dec as GLX_dec,   g.fuv_mag, g.fuv_magerr, g.nuv_mag,  g.nuv_magerr, g.E_bv,   g.objtype, g.fuv_flux, g.fuv_fluxerr, g.nuv_flux, g.nuv_fluxerr into mydb.FIRST_GALEX from MyDB.FIRST_Reduced_#p0#deg AS f    OUTER APPLY dbo.fGetNearestObjEq(f.ra, f.dec, #) AS x     JOIN photoobjall g ON g.objID = x.objID
